Package gui

Class PreAuctionerController

java.lang.Object
gui.PreAuctionerController
public class PreAuctionerController extends Object
The PreAuctionerController is class, which represents controller for auctioner. It implements functionality for auctioner to choose product and start auction with it. For access and easier implementation class contains Auctioner representing currently logger auctioner. AccountManager for access to functionalities for working with users and provide serialization. NftManager provides functionality for managing NFTs. Lastly class contains array of Auctions for upgrading list of auctions in process and array of UserMenuController for dynamic reloading of users gui.
